edu.uci.isr.impromptu.pocketpc
Interface PeerQueryProtocol

public interface PeerQueryProtocol

PeerQuery properties and commands used to compose the protocol PDUs, which are represented as YANCEES events by the application. This class basically stores those properties and types as constants.
